{"tid":2513283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖］冇錢就唔好學人放租","createTime":"2021-05-02T11:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T12:24:21.000Z","uid":281482,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"36144ec51c36240a16739e9f49ed33630247a42f","tid":2513283,"uid":281482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"<ins>幫人po</ins><br />\n冇啦啦要人退租 還鎖匙 之後唔撚退7000按金<br />\n自己應承咗今日俾到 然後話冇錢要等到九月先退<br />\n話要每個月一千咁退 邊會有人係咁樣退按金<br />\n仲要唔知佢到時係咪真係退到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後嘈嘈下就話要玩失蹤<br />\n查過層樓 唔係條友自己買<br />\n講嘢串柒柒又響度講埋啲大陸字 唔知裝乜鳩逼 <br />\n心諗得你經濟差？我屋企開善堂唔撚追得你數？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRExf2zaufMFE6vWkm5bYYQe15b7gX1kKBwzLL2pddgnJ?filename=tR3EAes.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtR3EAes.jpg&h=4e5065e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaerKzrhK6jCPs1GHL5qwwakL81jEfKC96MqUviPLuNkn?filename=u1C2x07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1C2x07.jpg&h=92c1955d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbABzDf6FUCQLRiWeyJLSRMhhQw6BNZ8EbXdyP8Zwfihf?filename=qHeMffd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHeMffd.jpg&h=cf5cc985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ7dyWeUQfR3wuCe9DhDpQm8z9AAbso7mjgi4RjiXZhvM?filename=NcuTEGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcuTEGU.jpg&h=c78da7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeKsbcag7qDetRKR4Brn3uMpCE2jL3KLnAN8WdHageU6E?filename=ZOpPXtz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOpPXtz.jpg&h=5c9764ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXntbJRVkxQCgDqxeh9EZcrkaEX17B7vS7HS25RPcLJLb?filename=TNGiQOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTNGiQOA.jpg&h=f1da7854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有錢買車 7000都唔肯還 <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmaa5kq9FTg5vkpZiUa3Ev4XjNk97Uts8C5RHvXnFDNrjP?filename=c15caEY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc15caEY.png&h=a7855258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n響度扮女人叫自己Mandy<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPJcStS7Q4Hg47E9TsFzuQEf7syy9zoa5tBd7ByqEHU4V?filename=4carZyu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4carZyu.png&h=2a5ff657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQtdAQVv1reuk45Aa2Xe1dpwiFSR7NDUpCRVEgpbazmFT?filename=aKKsJ6D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKKsJ6D.png&h=3ce039bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家小心呢位<strong>Mandy</strong><br />\n話唔定佢幫人課金充值呢啲都呃人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXgVKnnSr1jtGJQeX5HnwAFPNBsQeBaNZVsn7eUhrnFZg?filename=xt8k4fs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxt8k4fs.png&h=86361a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見你咁鍾意拍YouTube幫你宣傳埋又點話<br />\n幾時拍片教人呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申驚已報但唔知幾時先會做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbf0fece979e345238bcc3c6adda9159b50cdbd","tid":2513283,"uid":3206,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:30:52.000Z","msg":"tldr"},{"pid":"5cf3b50fec090fe6ccfcff9e7b9ebbdacf070737","tid":2513283,"uid":281482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"edbf0fece979e345238bcc3c6adda9159b50cdbd","tid":2513283,"uid":3206,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:30:52.000Z","msg":"tldr"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"